source and drain electrodes arranged on the interlayer insulating layer, the source and drain electrodes being electrically connected to source and drain regions respectively of the active layer through apertures in each of the interlayer insulating layer and the gate insulating layer;
a passivation layer arranged on the source and drain electrodes, and
a pixel electrode arranged on the passivation layer and being electrically connected to one of the source and drain electrodes through an aperture in the passivation layer.
